import React from 'react'
import { Table, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import PlayerBio from './players_bio.json'

const headerRow = ['Name', 'Team', 'Position', 'ID']

const renderBodyRow = ({ name, team, position, id }, i) => ({
  key: id,
  cells: [
    name,
    team,
    position,
    id
  ],
})

const PlayerTable = () => (
  <Segment basic padded='very'>
    <Table
      size='small'
      sortable
      color='purple'
      celled
      headerRow={headerRow}
      renderBodyRow={renderBodyRow}
      tableData={PlayerBio}
    />
  </Segment>
)

export default PlayerTable
